<taxonomicName box="[2273,2385,2547,2576]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Carpinus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="107" pageNumber="386" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="orientalis">orientalis</taxonomicName>
were placed under 
<taxonomicName box="[2070,2197,2587,2616]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Peromyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="107" pageNumber="386" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="nudipes">P. nudipes</taxonomicName>
. Seven subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
